S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Chart number
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: Chart number. Note, can be either paper chart number or ENC file name.

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Edition Date
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: Date of publishing for example of a publication, chart, or product.

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Last Notice Date
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: Date of the last notice to mariner, such as was applied to a chart or publication.

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: List Of Light Number
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: List of light number a navigational aid

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: ENC Name
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: The name of the ENC dataset. This is generally indicated in the dataset metadata (discovery or embedded) and will usually be the same as the name of the dataset file, possibly without the file extension component.

S100FC:listedValue.S100FC:label: operating anomalies identified within ECDIS including ENC issues
World Health Organization (WHO) health advisory information

S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:name: S124_Chart Affected
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:definition: National paper chart number or ENC name.

S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:name: Feature Reference
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:definition: Reference to an object or feature that is external to the dataset.

S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:name: General Area
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:definition: The general area used to identify which broad geographic region the message affects. The geographical name which is selected for the general area should be one that can be found on charts and in nautical publications. (S-53, 6).

S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:name: Locality
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:definition: Name and/or identifier of an area locality

S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:name: S124_Affected Chart Publications
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:definition: Identifies paper charts, ENCs or publications that are affected by the information.

S100FC:S100_FC_InformationAssociation.S100FC:name: Navigational Warning Preamble Content
S100FC:S100_FC_InformationAssociation.S100FC:definition: Association for the binding of navigational warning parts to the preamble

S100FC:S100_FC_FeatureAssociation.S100FC:name: TextAssociation
S100FC:S100_FC_FeatureAssociation.S100FC:definition: Acossiation for biding warning part to text placement
